Class StockItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.StockItem

  • public class StockItem
extends java.lang.Object

    StockItem Class to store information about the item

    Stores the name, ID, quantity, price, minimum stock, maximum stock, whether it can Expire, and if so the Date at which it will.
    Author:
